# Cosmic Ray mutation testing artifacts (per-module SQLite sessions,
# HTML reports, JSONL dumps). Regenerated by scripts/run_mutation_testing.sh
# and scripts/mutation/orchestrate.py.
#
# `cosmic-ray.toml` at the repo root IS committed — it is the canonical
# template documenting the operator-filter strategy. The orchestrator
# writes per-target TOMLs to a tempfile so this template is not
# clobbered. Per-PR `scripts/run_mutation_testing.sh` (legacy) DOES
# rewrite this file; if you commit changes, restore the template
# afterwards.
sessions/
scripts/mutation/sessions/
scripts/mutation/reports/

